    "### 2.2 MACD (Moving Average Convergence Divergence) - 指数平滑异同移动平均线\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 📖 术语解释\n",
    "\n",
    "**MACD（指数平滑异同移动平均线）** 是由Gerald Appel于1970年代提出的技术分析指标，用于捕捉趋势反转和动量变化。\n",
    "\n",
    "**计算公式**:\n",
    "```\n",
    "DIF = EMA(12) - EMA(26)      # 快线（12日EMA - 26日EMA）\n",
    "DEA = EMA(DIF, 9)            # 慢线（DIF的9日EMA）\n",
    "MACD = (DIF - DEA) × 2       # 柱状图\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**参数设置**:\n",
    "- 快线周期：12  \n",
    "- 慢线周期：26  \n",
    "- 信号线周期：9  \n",
    "- 这是MACD的默认参数设置（12/26/9）\n",
    "\n",
    "**判断标准**:\n",
    "- **DIF > DEA（金叉）**: 买入信号，多头趋势\n",
    "- **DIF < DEA（死叉）**: 卖出信号，空头趋势\n",
    "- **MACD > 0**: 多头市场\n",
    "- **MACD < 0**: 空头市场\n",
    "\n",
    "**作用**:\n",
    "1. 判断趋势方向（多头/空头）\n",
    "2. 识别趋势反转信号（金叉/死叉）\n",
    "3. 衡量趋势强度（MACD柱状图的高度）\n",
    "4. 识别顶背离和底背离\n",
    "\n",
    "**局限性**:\n",
    "- 在震荡市中，MACD可能频繁发出虚假信号\n",
    "- 对短期波动不敏感，存在滞后性"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "print('\\n2.2 计算MACD指标...')\n",
    "\n",
    "# MACD计算函数\n",
    "def calculate_macd(df, fast=12, slow=26, signal=9):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    计算MACD指标\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数:\n",
    "    - df: DataFrame，包含'close'列\n",
    "    - fast: 快线周期，默认12\n",
    "    - slow: 慢线周期，默认26\n",
    "    - signal: 信号线周期，默认9\n",
    "    \n",
    "    返回:\n",
    "    - df: 添加'MACD_DIF', 'MACD_DEA', 'MACD'列的DataFrame\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 计算EMA\n",
    "    ema_fast = df['close'].ewm(span=fast, adjust=False).mean()\n",
    "    ema_slow = df['close'].ewm(span=slow, adjust=False).mean()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算DIF（快线）\n",
    "    df['MACD_DIF'] = ema_fast - ema_slow\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算DEA（慢线）\n",
    "    df['MACD_DEA'] = df['MACD_DIF'].ewm(span=signal, adjust=False).mean()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算MACD柱状图\n",
    "    df['MACD'] = (df['MACD_DIF'] - df['MACD_DEA']) * 2\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return df\n",
    "\n",
    "# 计算MACD\n",
    "df_stock = calculate_macd(df_stock, fast=12, slow=26, signal=9)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'✓ MACD计算完成（参数: 12/26/9）')\n",
    "print(f'  当前DIF: {df_stock[\"MACD_DIF\"].iloc[-1]:.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'  当前DEA: {df_stock[\"MACD_DEA\"].iloc[-1]:.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'  当前MACD: {df_stock[\"MACD\"].iloc[-1]:.4f}')"
   ]
